they’re pretty cute. I am not going to critique the
show, the ridiculous characters, the target audience,
or other similar shows that have failed miserably
(Yes, “Cop Rock” comes to mind.) Instead I have
the pleasure to discuss a compact disc that is chock
full 0’ Catwalk songs, as well as a few other sur-
prises.

A Catwalk CD?? I don’t know who pushed for
this, but they have some guts. It may seem like a
reasonable thing to do; people must tune into the
show. My question is why waste money putting out
a recording when most of the show’s viewers just
want to watch the guitar player’s butt, or the bass
player’s bosoms, and see everybody get tangled up
in melodramatic love triangles. NOBODY LIKES

