emotional whiner without an accent. They’re back-
up singers that probably needed work after Clapton
went unplugged. As much as the band is deriva-
tive, they don’t sound like anybody. I mean, they

sound bad, but they sound “Catwalk” bad. Why is
it that T.V. bands don’t sound like anybody else,
but they all sound like each other?

