oh baby what did you do/ you hurt me.” You hear
this narrative and all you can think is “Don’t be a
chump, she’s gonna mess with your mind  she’s
gonna make a fool of you  she’s gonna, she’s
gonna hurt you!!!” I guess mistakes help you learn,
especially when it comes to love.

